# Local data — never commit (per-vault SQLite indexes etc.).
# Glob form (`data/*` rather than `data/`) keeps git recursing into the
# directory so the negation below actually fires.
data/*
# v1.7.5: bundled model-metadata seed JSON IS committed (anchor for offline /
# non-CI builds; refreshed at release time via release.yml + scripts/build-seed.mjs).
!data/seed-models.json
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-journal
*.db

